long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_GB,es,e:
Want to play T-Rex Chrome Dino Game? Play this game online for free in your own Chrome browser, no internet required. Lots of fun to play when bored at home or at school.

From now on you can play Dino Runner on Chrome browser easily, without internet, for free.

This extension brings Google's Dinosaur Game, also known as T-Rex Game and Dino Runner to your browser toolbar area.Simply press the action button and play it inside the popup area.You can press the Escape key to close the popup and stop the game .

T-Rex Dinosaur - a replica of the hidden game from Chrome offline mode.

How to play:
-  Press Space to start the game online and jump your Dino, use down arrow (↓) to duck.
